{"tid":227659,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"宣示主權？ 台灣「中華奧會」改名為「國家奧會」","createTime":"2017-05-03T10:45:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T15:00:05.000Z","uid":35790,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e13fe8862ed5ab174bccf59a9720483fcf0f100c","tid":227659,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:45:45.000Z","msg":"宣示主權？ 中華奧會改名「國家奧會」<br />\n<br />\n2017年05月03日 11:18&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n立法院教育及文化委員會今天審查「國民體育法」草案時，將「中華奧會」正名為「國家奧會」，這是跨出爭取更改中華奧會名稱的第一步！<br />\n<br />\n行政院版的國體法第五章名稱「中華奧會」，遭到立委諸公熱烈討論後，改為「國家奧會」，完全去「中華」化，立委林昶佐希望國體法先不再講死名稱、張廖萬堅認為，不要率先矮化自己，這樣的更改具有「主權、主體性」。<br />\n<br />\n經過立委商研後，國體法第二十六條修訂為「國家奧林匹克委員會（以下簡稱國家奧會）為法人，係經國際奧會承認之我國奧會代表。國家奧會之組織、任務及成立宗旨，應符合奧林匹克憲章，並受中華民國法律規範。」<br />\n<br />\n也就是這一條法條內，以前有寫到「中華奧會」的字眼，全部改為「國家奧會」。林昶佐表示，我們沒有違反國際奧會的規定，國際奧會說我們是什麼名稱就是那個名稱，但我們不必先框住自己。<br />\n(中時)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20170503002656-260407\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20170503002656-260407&d=ltJnWG3kir489%2BLnRwft2zACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=c0284381\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20170503002656-260407</a>"},{"pid":"9ca8126e092cfded02bd406f65ff6aef0e8dcd88","tid":227659,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:47:35.000Z","msg":"去中國化"},{"pid":"b039e02f6dce990c1305fdc4178340beff7eee34","tid":227659,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T11:08:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c514acfcb0b4bb58806a1e41224f3c7655a6b65","tid":227659,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T11:10:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00976e7600c09588c3d95c47112d3b7ad306253b","tid":227659,"uid":2373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T11:12:18.000Z","msg":"Very Good<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7012e479d21eddf74095575693c7652d677fbbc9","tid":227659,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T11:15:19.000Z","msg":"下到步改名稱 會旗 會歌？"},{"pid":"c7985423ed846fac5f3693f136db8b2040edf639","tid":227659,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T11:20:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3de38190e3da81e36e6fc42c3bd1ddd0180c8f4","tid":227659,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T11:21:52.000Z","msg":"支那兵敗如山倒"},{"pid":"7266a6c6226469009bf1c407911acb1dc2bcc409","tid":227659,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T11:52:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支那兵敗如山倒</blockquote><br />\n國民黨將會新黨化"},{"pid":"41ad58f578354cf7052acff4efdd96c1bbe56ee9","tid":227659,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T15:00:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}